&lt;p&gt;We’re seeking a seasoned and strategic administrative professional to help achieve our mission: Help humanity thrive by enabling the world’s teams to work together effortlessly.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role reports to a C-Suite Leader and partners closely with other ABP team members, delivering best-in-class support to our company leaders. Your Admin teammates will support you with partnership, resources, and knowledge-sharing to ensure your clientship helps your lead and their key stakeholders.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
