&lt;p&gt;At Asana, we’re building work management software to help every organization in the world become more effective in working together and realizing their goals. Our Business Development team plays a critical role in helping the world’s teams thrive by introducing them to Asana - as both a technology product and a holistic way of working.&lt;/p&gt;
