&lt;p&gt;We are entering a new era of work — one where AI agents collaborate alongside people to plan, act, and deliver outcomes at a scale and speed that wasn&#39;t possible before. At Asana, we call this Agentic Work Management: the orchestration of humans and AI agents toward shared goals, with full clarity on who is responsible for what, every step of the way. As a Corporate Account Executive, you will be at the forefront of this shift. You won&#39;t just be selling software — you&#39;ll be helping DACH organisations understand and solve their most pressing work management challenges, and guiding them toward a future where their teams and AI agents move together with purpose and trust.&lt;/p&gt;
