&lt;p&gt;Asana is evolving into a platform where humans and AI agents work together, and Core Integrations is helping make that platform more connected, extensible, and enterprise-ready. This team builds the extensible foundations and developer-facing capabilities that help customers, partners, and developers ensure Asana can meet their specific needs. We’re looking for a hands-on, technically strong Engineering Manager who thrives in ambiguity, cares deeply about developer experience, and can help a high-performing team ship high-quality products at the intersection of integrations, platform, and AI.&lt;/p&gt;
